HAPPY NEW YEAR TO ALL OF YOU  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Gnomish Advocate</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 7:37:43 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rude People</span><hr size=1> Auri: Younger server, and most people started playing at a time when they couldn't get ports. The people just starting are plenty rude, believe me. (For some reason, I'm trying to max my Faydwer factions when I get bored and am seeing the rudest of the lowbies in their native environments.) I'm toying with the idea of telling them all TLs now need portal chips. <p><a href="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=49189" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/whiz-banner-long-3.gif" height=60 width=468 alt="Whizbang Dustyboots" border=0></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=milaru>Milaru</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 7:43:14 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rude People</span><hr size=1> Bah, just send them to CT, I will buy you the portal chips if you promise to send the light elves there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukristalanorimkell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kristalan OrimKell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 7:53:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rude People</span><hr size=1> Ok.. Here is my story from just last week.  <br>
<br>
I was having a bad day already and was having to sit in East Commons trying to find someone to sell me SoW potions. (AC still has not given the ring up). I get a tell asking for a translocate to bind and offering to pay.  I tell them I do not have that spell and promptly get asked what kind of wizard am I to not have this spell?  Ok.. You can insult me, my dog, and my wife, you may even insult my guild and I will not go postal.. But no one insults my ability to be a wizard.  <br>
<br>
I do a who on my new found target for aggression.  Even better he is a warrior. (background: had a warrior the week before wanting 2k for the TL spell a couple of days before.) So I reply, &quot; I am sorry but I am not able to solo the mobs that drop that spell and seem to have trouble getting into those groups. I also did not have the 2k plat to pay for a spell that does not help me at all other then trying to make 2k plat. Good luck to you!&quot; <p><b><i>"Wizards come in two types.  Those with a twisted sense of humor and those with no sense of humor.  I have yet to decide which is more dangerous.."</b></i>
